## Constraints

- Live binding blocks authoritative export until bake resolves.
- Each capture profile must define schema, provenance, hash, route constraints, and rejection rules.
- Event conversion requires deterministic timing, resolved target paths, schema-valid values, and explicit collision policy.
- Do not allow sidecars or live captures to mutate timeline state directly.
- Do not add process lifecycle or output-format sidecar behavior.

